originalText.text: Not a bad company you can advance met some really nice people but be very very careful my experience was I was taken out of overseeing shoprite for deliveries and put into FedEx with no knowledge of what the position required not even the owner couldn't show me anything which led to bad service and numerous failures and for that I was terminated. Honestlyt hat was an unfair decision and the owner won't own up to that . If you work for them just be mindful of advancing  you will be set up to be let down this is coming from a person who's been through it. Good company but unprofessional ownership ijs

originalText.text: DO NOT use Same Day Delivery as a UPS Access Point. I dropped off a return package to ASOS. Normally the tall guy takes you to the back and scans it in front of you. This day an older woman was there and did not do that. I thought it was odd so I asked for a receipt and she said they did not provide one. Now there is no tracking information (UPS is still waiting for the package to be handed to them) and UPS can not locate the package. I called and the woman on the phone said she can not find the package and would call me back when her supervisor comes in. After a few hours I called and the same woman answered and said her supervisor checked and the package was handed to UPS. After speaking with ASOS I called Same Day Delivery back to asked for a receipt that I handed them the package. The same woman on the phone as before said she would have to wait for her manager to come in because he hasn’t arrived yet. So which one is it you liar? Did he not check for the package as you said he did on the second call and now you’re telling me he never arrived? I also find it very interesting that all the positive reviews this placed has received are all dated during the same time period, four months ago.

originalText.text: NEVER use this company.  Actually if you want your delivery to not get to the desired location on time you should go ahead and use them.  I called them at noon and asked for a delivery in 2 hours.  They said no problem.  If they delivered it by 5 pm i would have been happy but no such luck.  I called and they advised me that they never promised either 2 hours or 5 pm; rather they said they would do their best and they cant do better then that.  The driver probably decided to take a pot smoking break because he is nowhere to be found.  I have never written a review online until today.  That is how strongly I feel about these people and the awful service they provide.  BUYER BEWARE!!!!
